rows.label: qst000205_msg002
rows.name: Talulu, you got found today, mo?

rows.label: qst000205_msg003
rows.name:
Yes, mo... This person has a
talent for hide-and-seek, mo.

rows.label: qst000205_msg015
rows.name: Anyway, thanks for playing with us, mo!

rows.label: qst000205_msg005
rows.name: Mo mo? Aft, say thank you properly, mo.

rows.label: qst000205_msg006
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]I know, I know. Thanks
for playing with us.

rows.label: qst000205_msg007
rows.name:
My dad and mom are always so
busy, they never play with me...

rows.label: qst000205_msg008
rows.name:
But it was great playing together
today! It was really fun!

rows.label: qst000205_msg009
rows.name:
We can let you play with
us again sometime!

rows.label: qst000205_msg010
rows.name:
Um... this is a thank-you gift
from Kagege and friends, mo.

rows.label: qst000205_msg011
rows.name:
It's kind of like a piece
of our treasure, mo!

rows.label: qst000205_msg012
rows.name:
It might be junk, but we'd be
happy if you took it, mo.

rows.label: qst000205_msg013
rows.name: You probably have places to be, right?

rows.label: qst000205_msg014
rows.name:
Come play with us again
sometime! See ya!
